types of  elements 
1 : block level element 
2 : inline level element 

block level element 
1 : width 100% 
2 : always start from new line 
3 : it cannot contain block level element 
4 : by default padding and margin 
5 : seo based semantic tag 
6 : box rectangular or parent element
